_sText:
This a remake of a map I made a few months ago this one is more rounded and better quality over all.
This is my second release on FPSB

The map is made to be darker and is set during the night. the is a 16 player max on this map. the upper level features 2 hallway type structures that intersect at 3 points. on the top level you can go up on top of the median that separates the 2 hallways. On the lower level there is very little cover but almost complete darkness so you have to watch carefully for enemies.


Please list improvments for this map so i can add them to my future maps

I hope you enjoy 
thank you

Dr.A.0
